  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nHere's a plan to improve merge UX:\r\n\r\n- [x] deprecate the `--merge` flag, by enabling everything it does currently by default\r\n- [x] clean up the logs for merge-related functionality so that:\r\n  - if a Bellatrix epoch is set, we log loudly about the absence of EE endpoints, suggested fee recipients, etc\r\n  - if no Bellatrix epoch is set, we _do not_ log loudly about the absence of merge-related config (this might involve disabling some services that were previously enabled by the `--merge` flag)\r\n- [x] add an HTTP endpoint and/or routine log message to reassure users that their node is \"merge ready\", which checks the presence of all necessary flags\r\n",
